About
=====

pkgman is a package management tool which provides additional
functionality to basic package management utilities (pkgutils).

It appeared in an attempt to rewrite the prt-get tool, which is used
by CRUX: https://crux.nu/gitweb/?p=tools/prt-get.git;a=summary.


Dependencies
------------

- gcc8+
- make
- scdoc

